Skryti kurzoru 


One option would be to install unclutter.

Code: Select all

sudo apt update
sudo apt install unclutter

Then use this command:

Code: Select all

unclutter -idle 0

The mouse pointer will appear when moved.

The command can be put in autostart

Code: Select all

/etc/xdg/lxsession/LXDE-pi/autostart
